17:T48a,Internal evidence clearly defines this as a rigid urinary stone retrieval basket with shape-memory alloy construction and tipless design for use during rigid endoscopic procedures. The brochure description provides sufficient clinical detail: flexible shape-memory technology, tipless design for minimal trauma and clear visualization, and specific use case (rigid endoscopic stone removal). Classification shows 4.5 FR size, 55 cm length, 4-wire configuration. Entity type is product_family as this represents a specific basket design variant within the broader Ri-Catch system. Brand is marked missing but 'Ri-Catch+' is clearly indicated in product naming. Material is correctly identified as shape-memory alloy (likely Nitinol, standard for urological baskets). Review required due to: (1) missing brand confirmation from manufacturer catalog, (2) no external verification available, (3) need to confirm whether Ri-Catch+ is a distinct product line or size/configuration variant, (4) SKU examples absent for validation. Confidence 0.85 based on strong internal evidence but lack of external corroboration. No conflicts detected between available data points.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Ri-Catch+ Urinary Stone Retrieval Basket (Rigid)\",\"description\":\"Flexible shape-memory allows the basket to return to its original shape. Tipless design minimizes trauma and ensures clear visualization. Removes urinary stones during rigid endoscopic procedures.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Stone Baskets\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],[